iccut_v\">\n                <a href=\"\/a\/hot\/54ccfa1a3ee7ba8d_0.html?type=grap\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https:\/\/ww4.sinaimg.cn\/thumb180\/93f8d29dly1gch1pvxya2j21120ku7wj.jpg\" alt=\"\"><\/a>\n            <\/div>\n            <div class=\"list_des\">\n                <h3 class=\"list_title_s\"><a href=\"\/a\/hot\/54ccfa1a3ee7ba8d_0.html?type=grap\" class=\"S_txt1\" target=\"_blank\">Luna 纪录片<\/a><\/h3>\n                <div class=\"des_main S_txt2\">【MBC】Luna：“雪莉去天国之前曾联系过我，说想我，15年来第一次对我用了平语(非敬语)，她说‘欧尼吖，欧尼，我想你’，可以感受到是她忍了又忍，忍了很久才发来的信息，作为欧尼我感到很对不起”，“如果我可以先主动走向雪莉该多好，哪怕再多跟她说一句话该多好，再多对她说几次我爱你该多好”[泪]  ​​​​<\/div>\n            <\/div>\n        <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n    <div class=\"UG_box_foot\">\n        <a href=\"\/\/weibo.com\/a\/hot\/realtime\" class=\"S_txt1\" target=\"_blank\">查看更多<i class=\"W_ficon ficon_arrow_right S_ficon\">a<\/i><\/a>\n    <\/div>\n<\/div>\n"})</script>
